cdata.name: ZIX Token
cdata.desc:
Zeex is an online platform allowing for a simple and anonymous online shopping experience with cryptocurrencies. Zeex allows users to buy vouchers for specific vendors or online stores and makes them readily available to spend. As so, users can buy and sell their corporate currency (vouchers) and finally spend their cryptocurrency directly online.Zeex has relationships with 350+ global brands throughits sister company and can offer a seamless exchange of crypto to virtual gift cards for shops like Amazon,Foot Locker, Ticketmaster, XBOX, and more.
